  "title": "Draughtsman",
  "description": "<p>Draughtsman Job Ad</p><p>We are looking for a Draughtsman!</p><p>Do you love drawing by hand? Can you make perfect technical drawings with a pen and ruler?</p><p>Our small design studio makes custom furniture and works on old building repairs. We need a skilled person to draw our designs by hand.</p><p>What you'll do:</p><p>· Draw detailed building and furniture plans by hand (on paper).</p><p>· Help designers by turning their ideas into clear drawings.</p><p>· Make copies and keep old drawings organized.</p><p>· Sometimes visit buildings to measure and draw them.</p><p>Who you are:</p><p>· You have experience making hand-drawn technical plans.</p><p>· You are very good with drafting tools (pens, rulers, boards).</p><p>· You pay close attention to every small detail.</p><p>· You are organized and careful.</p><p>· Knowing a little CAD (like AutoCAD) is a plus.</p><p>What we offer:</p><p>· A quiet studio where drawing by hand is important.</p><p>· Interesting projects.</p><p>· A good team to work with.</p><p>· Fair pay.<br />4 off days monthly, rest days depend on schedule</p><p>Competitive salary 3k and above</p><p>Positive and nurturing working environment</p><p>Work location: orchard</p><p>Duration: permanent</p><p>Requirements</p><p>Qualifications - diploma or high school diploma</p><p>Work experience- at least one year working experience in related fields</p><p>Job type- full time</p><p>Required languages: English and able to communicate with mandarin speaking customers</p><p>Job specialisation- services, personal care</p><p>If you have an interest in applying for this role, please WhatsApp me at 98198786 to apply. Only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Priority will be given to Singaporeans</p><p>Young hon Lim/ manager</p><p>Render private limited</p><p>EA licence no 15c7827</p><p>EA reg no R1550906</p>",
